text: Ellis Lorenzo Webster is an Anguillan politician. He was the 2nd Premier of the British Overseas Territory of Anguilla from 2020 - 2025. He was first elected when he led the Anguilla Progressive Movement to victory in the 2020 general election.Dr. Ellis Lorenzo Webster sworn in, as APM takes over in Anguilla, Anguilla News, July 1, 2020 ==References== ==Other websites== * Ellis Webster at caribbeanelections.com Category:Premiers of Anguilla Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
